    <section>
      <h2>History</h2>
      <p>Since 2005, White Water Rafting Co. has grown from a small local group of river lovers into a full rafting company known for quality experiences and excellent service. Over the years, we’ve guided hundreds of groups, invested in top equipment, and worked hard to preserve the river environments we raft.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Adventure Awaits You!</h2>
      <p>Whether you seek calm floats or thrilling rapids, family rafting or challenging routes, we have trips designed for all levels. Browse our Trips page to discover the adventure that's right for you.</p>
